== 生平 ==
安德烈·維爾切於1963年生於[[列寧格勒|列寧格勒]]（現稱「聖彼得堡」）<ref name="TerrorismoOccidentale">{{cite book|last1=Chomsky|first1=Noam|author-link1=Noam Chomsky|last2=Vltchek|first2=Andre|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BspECgAAQBAJ&pg=PT1|chapter=Presentazione|title=Terrorismo occidentale|publisher=Ponte alle Grazie|year=2015|isbn=978-88-6833-466-6|quote=Andre Vltchek è nato a Leningrado nel 1963 ed è cresciuto a Plzeň, in Cecoslovacchia, prima di trasferirsi a New York.|language=it|access-date=2022-04-23|archive-date=2022-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512091240/https://books.google.com/books?id=BspECgAAQBAJ&pg=PT1}}</ref>，父親是捷克核物理學家，母親是畫家。<ref name="legrandsoir">{{cite web|title=Point de non-retour|url=http://www.legrandsoir.info/Point-de-non-retour.html?var_mode=calcul|date=September 1, 2010|work=Le Grand Soir|language=fr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409074659/http://www.legrandsoir.info/Point-de-non-retour.html?var_mode=calcul|archive-date=2014-04-09}}</ref>成年后移居美国，改为美国国籍。<ref name="tt">{{cite web|title=Freedom of speech has become a propaganda slogan: Andre Vltchek|url=http://www.tehrantimes.com/world/101265-freedom-of-speech-has-become-a-propaganda-slogan-andre-vltchek|date=2012-09-05|last=Ziabari|first=Kourosh|work=[[Tehran_Times|Tehran Times]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714155114/http://www.tehrantimes.com/world/101265-freedom-of-speech-has-become-a-propaganda-slogan-andre-vltchek|archive-date=2014-07-14|url-status=dead}}</ref>

從八十年代開始，維爾切擔任戰地記者與攝影師遊歷了140多個國家，報導了[[波斯尼亞戰爭|波斯尼亞戰爭]]、[[秘鲁内部冲突|秘魯內戰]]、[[斯里蘭卡內戰|斯里蘭卡內戰]]、[[剛果戰爭|剛果戰爭]]、[[東帝汶|東帝汶]]等戰爭。<ref name="mrzine"/><ref name="cd">{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/cndy/2011-10/12/content_13873914.htm|title=China offers vital alternative to West|first=Cheng|last=Guangjin|work=[[China_Daily|China Daily]]|date=2011-10-12|access-date=2016-04-02|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924044402/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/cndy/2011-10/12/content_13873914.htm|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="oak">{{cite web|title=Aceh Abandoned: The Second Tsunami|url=https://www.oaklandinstitute.org/aceh-abandoned-second-tsunami-0|date=2005-02-01|last=Vltchek|first=Andre|publisher=[[Oakland_Institute|Oakland Institute]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104235617/https://www.oaklandinstitute.org/aceh-abandoned-second-tsunami-0|archive-date=2017-01-04|quote=Andre Vltchek, a Senior Fellow at the Oakland Institute}}</ref>並曾為[[朝日新聞|朝日新聞]]、[[明鏡|明鏡]]、[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]、[[新聞週刊|新聞週刊]]、[[人民日報|人民日報]]、[[中國日報|中國日報]]、CounterPunch 等刊物撰寫文章。<ref name="oak"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://travel.cnn.com/author/andre-vltchek/|title=Author: Andre Vltchek|work=CNN Travel|quote=Andre is also a Senior Fellow at The Oakland Institute.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104234436/http://travel.cnn.com/author/andre-vltchek/|archive-date=2017-01-04}}</ref>

維爾切在2011年10月於人民日報海外版發表文章《西方完善攻擊中國的技術》。<ref>{{Cite news |url = http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15853517.html |title = 美国记者：西方完善攻击中国的技术 |date         = 2011年10月11日 |accessdate   = 2020-03-04 |archive-date = 2012-06-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120605184943/http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15853517.html |dead-url     = yes |newspaper  = 人民日報海外版 |via  = 人民网}}</ref>同月他接受人民日報訪問，標題為《美國作家安德烈︰我為什麼要為中國說好話》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15901135.html |title=美國作家安德烈︰我為什麼要為中國說好話 |accessdate=2020-03-04 |archive-date=2011-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111017083438/http://world.people.com.cn/GB/15901135.html |website=人民网 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.people.cn/90883/7617555.html |title=US novelist: China should demand more respect from West |accessdate=2020-03-04 |date=October 14, 2011 |archive-date=2020-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304021127/http://en.people.cn/90883/7617555.html |dead-url=no |website=人民网 }}</ref>。

2020年9月22日，維爾切在車裡死去，享年57岁。土耳其警方将他的死亡记录为“可疑”，正在調查死因。<ref name=":0" />維爾切的妻子表示他死於糖尿病并发症。他的死在中國大陸引起巨大迴響和陰謀論。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Death of US journalist who defended Beijing hits hard in China|url=https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/politics/article/3103989/death-pro-china-us-journalist-sparks-grief-and-conspiracy|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2020-10-02|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423083819/https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/politics/article/3103989/death-pro-china-us-journalist-sparks-grief-and-conspiracy}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
美國語言學家[[諾姆·喬姆斯基|諾姆·喬姆斯基]]在評論維爾切2010年出版的《大洋洲》一書時說，這書它喚起了「當代世界的現實」，並且「他成功地追溯到那些痛苦和可恥的歷史根源，尤其是指向西方的」。<ref name="cd2">{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/cndy/2011-10/12/content_13873914.htm|title=China offers vital alternative to West|first=Cheng|last=Guangjin|work=[[China_Daily|China Daily]]|date=2011-10-12|access-date=2016-04-02|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924044402/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/cndy/2011-10/12/content_13873914.htm|url-status=live}}</ref>

